Just a clean Eagle Globe and Anchor on a 40yr veteran. Sometimes it’s not all about the big fancy tattoos and it’s all about the mark itself and the story it holds. 

We get caught up in the glitz and glam of trying to be special on the internet for a little bit of notariaty…. But god damn if these aren’t the tattoos that keep me on planet earth and mean so much to me. 

I am a proud veteran and I love working with soldiers and veterans. Being able to leave their mark on them that will show their story in life is truly a passion of mine. 

Thank you for your service. 🇺🇸

When you get hung up in life and things aren’t working take a moment and just stop, step back and take a sincere look at what’s happening in your life 

Pivot - from what your doing and change course

Re-think - about your path and how it’s working and where you would rather be heading

Re-imagine - where you can picture yourself in the moment you truly feel want to be in and manifest (with adding hard work) towards this goal

Just a lil reminder that you are never truly stuck where you are at… anyone can change their stars

#motivation #yournotstuck #chooseanotherpath #choicesareeverywhere #motivationalquotes #motivational #inspiration #motivationalspeaker #speakfromtheheart #ryaneternal

This whole life hasn’t been perfect by any means but I’ve done the best to right all my wrongs and find the calm in myself

Getting older is a pretty wild ride and at some point you step back and just gear down and start really taking it all in and really appreciating the little things that aren’t so little anymore… cause one day it’s all going to be gone and we will just be stories told by the following generations

I guess I’ve been deep diving into all these thoughts and just have grown to really not be the man I started out in life, I was angry at the world and angry at my father and angry for just being angry because I didn’t know what else to do with my emotions.

I’d like to apologize to anyone I hurt along the way that I haven’t had the chance to apologize to face to face. I’m trying daily and being a much better human to anyone and everyone that comes in my path because I just wanna exit this earth a long time from now with a lot of amazing stories about the ways I helped people and changed their lives because of the good I caused.

We all have our stories and I guess what I’m getting at is how do you want your story to unravel.
